ion disk. Further high resolution near-infrared spectra are currently\nbeing obtained to confirm the proposed geometry and kinematics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jun 2003 10:04:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Oct 2003 10:33:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
